#### TC-E001: User Registration and Login

**Scenario**: Complete user journey from signup to login

**Test**:
```typescript
test('user can register and login', async ({ page }) => {
  // Navigate to signup
  await page.goto('/signup');

  // Fill registration form
  await page.fill('#email', 'test@example.com');
  await page.fill('#name', 'Test User');
  await page.fill('#password', 'SecurePass123!');
  await page.click('#submit-button');

  // Verify redirect to dashboard
  await page.waitForURL('/dashboard');
  await expect(page.locator('#welcome-message')).toContainText('Welcome, Test User');

  // Logout
  await page.click('#logout-button');

  // Login again
  await page.goto('/login');
  await page.fill('#email', 'test@example.com');
  await page.fill('#password', 'SecurePass123!');
  await page.click('#login-button');

  // Verify logged in
  await page.waitForURL('/dashboard');
});
```

#### TC-E002: Create and View Resource

**Scenario**: User creates a post and views it

**Test**:
```typescript
test('user can create and view post', async ({ page }) => {
  // Login first
  await loginAs(page, 'test@example.com', 'password');

  // Create post
  await page.goto('/posts/new');
  await page.fill('#title', 'My First Post');
  await page.fill('#content', 'Post content here...');
  await page.click('#publish-button');

  // Verify redirect to post page
  await page.waitForURL(/\/posts\/\d+/);

  // Verify post content
  await expect(page.locator('h1')).toContainText('My First Post');
  await expect(page.locator('.content')).toContainText('Post content here...');
});
```
