### Load Testing

**Tool**: Artillery

**Scenario**: API load test

```yaml
# load-test.yml
config:
  target: "https://api.example.com"
  phases:
    - duration: 60
      arrivalRate: 10
      name: "Warm up"
    - duration: 120
      arrivalRate: 50
      name: "Load test"

scenarios:
  - name: "User flow"
    flow:
      - post:
          url: "/api/auth/login"
          json:
            email: "test@example.com"
            password: "password"
      - get:
          url: "/api/users/me"
```

**Run**:
```bash
artillery run load-test.yml
```

**Acceptance Criteria**:
- p95 response time < 200ms
- Error rate < 1%
- Can handle 1000 concurrent users
